411
00:27:21,425 --> 00:27:25,660
Farei chover caos,

412
00:27:25,696 --> 00:27:29,664
mesmo que me atinja,

413
00:27:29,700 --> 00:27:32,367
porque prefiro vê-lo perder

414
00:27:32,402 --> 00:27:35,603
do que eu ganhar.

415
00:27:41,812 --> 00:27:44,345
É todo o tempo que tenho.

416
00:27:46,416 --> 00:27:47,916
<i>A 9 de maio, deitámos abaixo</i>

417
00:27:47,951 --> 00:27:50,852
<i>o maior conglomerado do mundo.</i>

418
00:27:50,887 --> 00:27:52,787
<i>Todos tínhamos a mesma intenção...</i>

419
00:27:52,823 --> 00:27:56,758
<i>Eu, Darlene, Mobley,
Trenton, Romero...</i>

420
00:27:56,793 --> 00:27:58,693
<i>Mudar o mundo.</i>

421
00:27:58,729 --> 00:28:00,562
<i>Mas havia outro jogador,</i>

422
00:28:00,597 --> 00:28:02,363
<i>o Dark Army.</i>

423
00:28:02,399 --> 00:28:05,200
<i>Nunca chegámos a saber
quais eram as suas intenções.</i>

424
00:28:08,238 --> 00:28:10,205
<i>Um Pwn Phone da Pwnie Express.</i>

425
00:28:10,240 --> 00:28:12,010
<i>Um telemóvel carregado</i>

426
00:28:12,015 --> 00:28:14,442
<i>com 103 ferramentas
